replies.bodyText:
I'm leaving the false for emphasis, although nothing ever changes it in the rest of the tests (maybe some code was removed at some point). Adding the following comment to explain:
 // don't skip blobs because otherwise when reimporting documents the
 // "data" field is interpreted as (invalid) base64 instead of a filename

